Class DomEvent<H extends EventHandler>

Type Parameters:
H - handler type
All Implemented Interfaces:
HasNativeEvent
Direct Known Subclasses:
BlurEvent, CanPlayThroughEvent, ChangeEvent, ContextMenuEvent, DragDropEventBase, EndedEvent, ErrorEvent, FocusEvent, GestureChangeEvent, GestureEndEvent, GestureStartEvent, HumanInputEvent, KeyEvent, LoadedMetadataEvent, LoadEvent, LoseCaptureEvent, ProgressEvent, ScrollEvent
public abstract class DomEvent<H extends EventHandler> extends GwtEvent<H> implements HasNativeEvent
DomEvent is a subclass of GwtEvent that provides events that underlying native browser event object as well as a subclass of DomEvent.Type that understands GWT event bits used by sinkEvents().
